    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the wife organized it so-- so many plates towards the wall, to get-- to quiet them down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I must admit that I've got these moments, because not only [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] going further away from Holland to Spain, but also, when I came back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All this together makes me very nervous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
